    <item>
      <title>花旗指出欧洲股市的三大潜在催化剂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/citi-cites-three-potential-catalysts-for-european-stocks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团欧洲、中东和非洲地区研究主管 Elise Badoy 表示，现在可能是平仓欧洲股票的时机，她指出，乌克兰可能停火、关税更加明朗以及中国经济数据改善都是催化剂。她在彭博电视上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/citi-cites-three-potential-catalysts-for-european-stocks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:49:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲贷款银行家寄希望于并购复苏以提高贷款量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/europe-s-loan-bankers-pin-hopes-on-m-a-revival-to-boost-volumes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[再融资有助于在 2024 年增加欧洲的贷款量，但随着并购活动似乎终于开始回暖，银行家们相信过桥融资的形势终于出现好转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/europe-s-loan-bankers-pin-hopes-on-m-a-revival-to-boost-volumes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国推出减债措施以偿还 260 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/thailand-unveils-debt-relief-measures-to-cover-26-billion-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国出台了一系列新的债务减免措施，为数百万难以偿还贷款的零售借款人和小企业提供援助，这是泰国当局为解决东南亚最高家庭债务水平而采取的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/thailand-unveils-debt-relief-measures-to-cover-26-billion-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:07:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
