      <title>前摩根大通交易员被指控欺诈，称自己被错误解雇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-jpmorgan-trader-accused-of-spoofing-says-he-was-wrongly-fired</link>
