      <title>法国电力公司上调2024年核电发电量目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/edf-raises-target-for-2024-nuclear-power-production-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国电力公司今年第二次上调了法国核电产量目标，理由是该公司在管理电厂维护停机以及破裂管道的检查和修复方面取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/edf-raises-target-for-2024-nuclear-power-production-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国市场谨慎，关键政策会议希望减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-markets-flag-caution-reduced-hope-for-key-policy-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国市场再次出现一种熟悉的怀疑情绪，股市涨势快速消退，表明人们对此次重要政策会议能否出台当局承诺的那种有力增长刺激措施的预期较低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-markets-flag-caution-reduced-hope-for-key-policy-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
